\par\pard\plain \tx1123\tx1685\tx2246\tx2794\tx3355\tx3917\tx4478\tx5040\tx5602\tx6163\tx6725\fi720\ri-720\sl288\slmult1\ql\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Mandri started to speak, then gave pause to give the question good consideration. And it seemed Moteah was actually interested in the answer, skeptical though she was. He decided, in the end, that if she had any self doubt he should strike at it. This wasn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t some strategy to wiggle out of his Minder\u8217\'92s grip, this was just the kind of thing Mandri liked to do. She deserved it anyways.}
