\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Seb rushed by Mandri\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s room, then came back, noticing the fresh new vantage punched into the foot of the wall.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Move out of the way!\u8221\'94 she shouted as she ran in. She kicked Mandri\u8217\'92s hip, then squatted down and started firing arrows at the marching men. They were close enough now that their eyes could be seen peering over their shields.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Seb fired her arrows with ruthless efficiency, but judging by the stream of curses that followed every shot, she was missing her mark. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Seb grabbed her bow in both hands and snapped it on her knee. She tossed the kindling at Mandri and pulled her dagger, then fled from the room.}
